attributes.title: Atrocious app for an atrocious orange sociopath
attributes.review: There are few words to describe the way I feel about the disgraceful state of this country. Donald Trump, who conned his way into the presidency, promised to “make America great again”. He wants to claim great economic achievements, but what has he actually “achieved” during his pitiful sham of a reign? Higher taxes for workers and the middle class? Heightening racial tensions and linking arms with far-right bigots? Making friends with murderous dictators? Destroying the environment? Encouraging police brutality? The list goes on. This ignorant, arrogant, privileged piece of garbage has been formally impeached by the House of Representatives for abuses of power and obstruction of Congress. He has also been credibly suspected of countless other acts of malfeasance, from misusing campaign funds all the way up to committing treason by enlisting a foreign government to interfere with a presidential election. VOTE HIM OUT.
